com.alcatel_lucent.nz.wnmsextract
Class WNMSDataScheduler

java.lang.Object
  com.alcatel_lucent.nz.wnmsextract.WNMSDataScheduler

public class WNMSDataScheduler
extends java.lang.Object

Multi threaded application entry point for WNMS parsing. This Class (the othet MAIN class) has fallen into disuse. It could be revived if the app is ever run on a server with a decent amount of RAM but at present any more than a single thread will throw OutOfMemor errors. :(

Author:
jnramsay TODO FTP client for as a connector type TODO Jar-in-Jar classloading (!) - Not practical TODO Debug messed up parser type allocation
